title: Grateful Dead Live at The Capitol Centre on 1990-03-16
lineage: Playback of MCs recording deck (Marantz PMDxxx) > Sony D6 > Maxell XL90s (1st gen). 1st (gen) > Playback on Marantz PRD505 (azimuth adjusted) > Marantz Intergrated Stereo Amp MP-68 > SB Audigy4 on new P4 machine > Sound Forge normalization > WAV > CDWave > WAVs > Flacfrontend 1.7.1 (level 8) > flacs.
description:
Disc 1

Set 1

01. Crowd/tuning
02. Let The Good Times Roll
03. Touch Of Grey
04. New Minglewood Blues
05. Peggy-O
06. Queen Jane Approxmately
07. Loser
08. Black Throated Wind (new words)
09. Birdsong
10. Blow Away

Disc 2

Set 2

01. Crowd/tunng
02. Scarlet Begonias
03. Fire On The Mountain (instrumental)
04. Estimated Prophet
05. Ship Of Fools
06. Women Are Smarter (mariba jam, Eyes tease)
07. Drums /
08. / Space
09. The Other One
10. Stella Blue
11. Sugar Magnolia

Encore

12. The Last Time
